wearing velvet slippers under a golden umbrella ( burmese : ကတ တီပါ ဖိနပ စီး ရွှေထီးဆောင း , pronounced as katipa phanat see shwe htee hsaung ) is a 1970 burmese film directed by maung wunna starring myat mon , myat lay and thet naung . the film was maung wunna 's first feature as director and he also wrote the screenplay , based on the novel of the same name by maung thara .